Defendant David R Rockman in court with Attorney Eric Theodore Raskopf.  Michele W. Hulgaard appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  Case called for sentencing hearing.  State gives sentencing recommendations.  Attorney Raskopf makes statements regarding sentencing.  Defendant makes statements.  Court sentences the Defendant to the following:

COUNT #1:   WITHHELD SENTENCE

TERM OF PROBATION:  1 YEAR

CONDITIONS OF PROBATON:  
____AODA Assessment and follow through with any treatment recommended;
____Absolute Sobriety;  Random U.A.'s ; 
____Follow through with any treatment and/or counseling recommended by Agent;
____Maintain employment and/or combination of schooling 
____Attend 1 alumni meeting per month

COSTS:  $243.00 (to be paid out of cash bail posted - remainder to be refunded to poster)
